description.translate:
$(b;summer)Titania$() holds the title of the $(b;spring)Fairy Queen$(), thou a self proclaimed name. Claimed after a everlasting war between light and darkness.
 Though intimidating I know Queen Titania likes to indulge herself, so a $(b;autumn)Honey Glazed$() ham would be a perfect $(b;spring)gift$(), for the leader of the Golden Court. Don't you agree, darling?

description.text: That looks absolutely scrumptious! This should appease a Queen!
